		<DisplayName>Companion</DisplayName>
		<Backstory>It is common for Elven magicians to try to immerse themselves in their environment in a spiritual way by meditating in places filled with life. This helps them achieve the mind-world unity they so strive for - to be aware of all things is required to fully appreciate the gift of life. This ability is highly prized in the Elvish society and normally, a truly honed empathic ability would have marked Companion out as a leader.

Companion has unfortunately taken this philosophy too far. She has so honed her empathic abilities and spent so much time immersed in the meditative trance that she has essentially lost her own personality. Her tremendously open mind and spirit makes it a pure pleasure to be in her presence because she can offer unconditional love to all living things. For this reason she has become adored by elementals and forest creatures alike. When it comes to making decisions and carrying them out, Companion is of no use to anyone.</Backstory>
